<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Nail Cutter Shop</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #0077cc;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .product {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .product img {
      width: 250px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .details {
      max-width: 500px;
    }

    h2 {
      color: #0077cc;
    }

    .price {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #111;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 15px;
      background-color: #0077cc;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #005fa3;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      color: #555;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>✨ Premium Nail Cutters ✨</h1>
    <p>Sharp. Durable. Stylish.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="product">
      <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/63/Nail_clipper.jpg/320px-Nail_clipper.jpg" alt="Nail Cutter">
      <div class="details">
        <h2>Stainless Steel Nail Cutter</h2>
        <p>
          Perfect for everyday grooming — our premium stainless-steel nail cutter is designed for clean, precise cuts every time. 
          Compact, comfortable to hold, and rust-resistant.
        </p>
        <p class="price">$5.99</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn">🛒 Buy Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2025 NailCutterShop | Designed with 💙 for your care</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
